00:18:27,620 --> 00:18:31,160
 Da mu dođemo i kažemo evo ne.

154
00:18:35,160 --> 00:18:41,120
 Duše sve ti na poj srce povjere.

155
00:18:41,120 --> 00:18:45,580
 Gdje god zoveš taj da krene.

156
00:18:45,580 --> 00:18:50,780
 Po morima da hodam.

157
00:18:51,780 --> 00:18:53,400
 Ti me volim.

158
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:57,260
 Ti gdje su največe dubine.

159
00:18:57,260 --> 00:19:01,040
 Ti živi, drugi sine.

160
00:19:01,040 --> 00:19:05,700
 Znam da spasim te ne ovdje.

